com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.exporter.server

Class SnomedRefSetExporterQueries

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.exporter.server.SnomedRefSetExporterQueries

  • public abstract class SnomedRefSetExporterQueries
extends java.lang.Object
    These queries are executed during the reference set export.

    Note: Most joins assume a 1:1 mapping from CDO IDs to reference set identifier concept IDs; this means that once a reference set has been created, its identifier concept ID may not change during its lifetime (separate branches may create different reference set instances with the same ID, though).
